    "extract": "Leong Mun Wai is a Singaporean politician and former investment banker who served as Secretary-General of the Progress Singapore Party between 2023 to 2024 and re-elected since 2025 and as a Non-Constituency Member of Parliament (NCMP) between 2020 to 2025.",
    "extract_html": "<p><b>Leong Mun Wai</b> is a Singaporean politician and former investment banker who served as Secretary-General of the Progress Singapore Party between 2023 to 2024 and re-elected since 2025 and as a Non-Constituency Member of Parliament (NCMP) between 2020 to 2025.</p>"
